text: thumb| Website: https://www.meziklasi.cz/ Meziklasí is a small village, part of Dolní Město in the Havlíčkův Brod district of the Czech Republic. It is situated about 2,5 km northwest of the Dolní Město. In the 2009 there were registered 42 addresses. In 2001 there lived 58 residents. Meziklasí is also name of the cadastral area with an area of 3,88 km2. Category:Villages in Havlíčkův Brod District
